вҚқ MultiLineLiterals.tc
вҚқ в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

)CLEAR
CLEAR WS

вҚқ NOTE: immediate execution: Command::process_line()
вҚқ       вҺ•FX:                 UserFunction::transform_old_multi_line_strings()
вҚқ                            UserFunction::transform_new_multi_line_strings()
вҚқ                            UserFunction::transform_multi_line_literals()


вҚқ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ LITERAL in Function в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

вҲҮFOO
 "Line 1"
 QвҶҗ<<<
 211 212 213 214
 221 'a' 223 224
 231 232 233 234
   >>>
Q
